hello developers,

I found the project is use IBM JDK,and for most other users, maybe they 
are useing Sun JDK.

The word "assert" was used as a keyword in Sun JDK 1.4.2 and some classes 
can't be compiled by Sun JDK.


How can I compile the project use Sun JDK 1.4.2?

zhousp
